fields.name: Abbey 144a Predator Summer Gun Gas 700ml
fields.description:
A very popular selling gas especially during summer and in countries that have warmer climates. This gas really is a low-power gas. It has a high silicone content, so you will need to clean your GBB Airsoft weapon more frequently to ensure longevity. 

Stocked and used by our Patrol Base workshop and other staff members for years, each can has 700ml of contents and can be used to reduce the output power of a hot gas gun, or ensure the smooth silky operation of a Polymer slid pistol.

- Weaker Than Ultra Gas
- Ideal Summer Gas
- 700ml Content

fields.name: Abbey Predator Maintenance Gas 144A 270ml

Please note this is not a guaranteed item to repair leaky magazines, but so far we have been impressed with its success rate. We have used this in-store many times and repaired many magazines with slow leaks.

- Extra Lubricated
- Super Compact

fields.name: TMC M67 PVC Patch
fields.description:
A PVC Patch with a velcro-back, that is designed to sit on Hats, Rigs, Backpacks, or anywhere with a free space of Velcro. The patch features an M67 Fragmentation Grenade as used by the United States Armed Forces, and is the perfect finishing touch to any loadout.

fields.name: TMC M433 PVC Patch
fields.description:
A PVC velcro-backed 3D effect morale patch which features a 40mm HEDP M433 grenade, that is perfect for placing on Hats, Rigs, Backpacks or anywhere with free velcro space. The 40mm HEDP M433 is a High Explosive Dual Purpose grenade that has the ability to penetrate 2 inches of Steel Armour in the real world, making it a nice balance of Anti-Personnel and Anti-Material. 

- PVC 3D Patch
- Velcro Backed
- 40mm Grenade

fields.name: Patch Lab Polish SF SMG-5 3D PVC Morale Patch Limited Edition
fields.description:
Looking for a way to broadcast your national pride or your love for CYMA and Taiwangun? The Patch Lab Polish SF SMG-5 3D PVC morale patch depicts a fully kitted out elite Polish operator packing a custom SMG-5 which looks a lot like the CM.041G. The patch is constructed from PVC with raised and recessed detail to create a 3D effect and has a subdued colour scheme of olive and grey. The Polish flag on the operator's helmet is in full colour, as are the CYMA and Taiwangun logos on teeny, tiny patches attached to the operator's dangler pouch. The level of detail in this patch is rather impressive, and it would look awesome with practically any loadout.

- Limited edition 3D PVC patch
- Velcro backed
- Depicts a GROM operator and CYMA fan!

fields.name: JTG Dare To Be Unique PVC Morale Patch
fields.description:
Style up your Airsoft kit with this unique, to say the least, patch from JTG! The patch is constructed from PVC and has a 3D effect and depicts a creature of some form that appears to be derived from a Seahorse and a Unicorn. Creepy, but some might find it cute, and it certainly is unique! What better way to mark yourself out from the crowd than by wearing this patch? The masses, with their boring olive green and tan patches depicting everyday things such as national flags, won't know what hit them when they lay eyes on this patch!

- 3D PVC Patch
- Velcro backed
- Depicts a Seahorse-Unicorn hybrid creature
